# Adding New Pages: Sitemap & Ellmo-AI Guide

## Sitemap
- **Auto-included**: Static marketing pages (auto-indexed)
- **Excluded**: Dashboard (`/dashboard/*`), API routes (`/api/*`)
- **Manual addition**: Add to `additionalPaths` in `next-sitemap.config.js` for dynamic/static hybrids
- **Separate sitemaps**: Blog uses `src/app/blog/sitemap.ts`

## Ellmo-AI Content
- **Add `<EllmoContent />`**: Marketing/landing pages for AI personalization (SEO & AEO)
- **Middleware**: Auto-tracks all non-API page visits for analytics

## Checklists
**Marketing Page** (`/new-feature`):
- [ ] Create `src/app/new-feature/page.tsx`
- [ ] Add to `additionalPaths` if page is not automatically added to the sitemap
- [ ] Include `<EllmoContent />`
- [ ] Test: `npm run build && npm run postbuild`

**User Page** (`/dashboard/settings`):
- [ ] Create component (auto-excluded from sitemap)
- [ ] Skips `<EllmoContent />`
- [ ] Add authentication guards

